This '''[[Mos Eisley/Legends|Mos Eisley]] beggar''' was one of the spaceport's many destitute citizens forced to live in the streets and beg for money.<ref name="CCG" />

The [[Human/Legends|Human]] beggar was present in the streets of the spaceport when [[Obi-Wan Kenobi/Legends|Obi-Wan Kenobi]], [[Luke Skywalker/Legends|Luke Skywalker]], [[C-3PO/Legends|C-3PO]] and [[R2-D2/Legends|R2-D2]] passed by on their way to [[Docking Bay 94/Legends|Docking Bay 94]] and the ''[[Millennium Falcon/Legends|Millennium Falcon]]'' shortly before the [[Battle of Yavin/Legends|Battle of Yavin]]. Moments later, a contingent of Imperial [[Stormtrooper/Legends|stormtroopers]] marched by to intercept Kenobi and the others.<ref name="ANH" />

